# string-concat

Non-numeric hot path — string concatenation + `.length`, exercising the
String intrinsics rather than the long/double JIT lanes.

```scalascript
def label(n: Int): String = "item-" + n

def workload(): Long =
  var total = 0L
  var i = 0
  while i < 20000 do
    total = total + label(i).length
    i = i + 1
  total
```
